| <math>x(t)=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}X(f)\ e^{i2\pi ft}\,df</math> ||<math>x[n]=T_s\int_{1/T_s}\bar{X}(f)\ e^{i2\pi fnT_s}\ df</math>
